  <title>Best Hair Salon Pittsburgh PA | Craft Collective Salon Group</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Pittsburgh's top-rated hair salon specializing in highlights, balayage, blonding, dimensional color, precision haircuts, keratin treatments, and hair extensions. Located in North Hills on Babcock Blvd, serving greater Pittsburgh and Canonsburg. Award-winning stylists led by Wella Professionals artist Derek Piekarski." />
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
