  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <p class="section-label">Common Questions</p>
      <h2 id="faq-heading" class="section-headline">Frequently <em>asked</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item open">
        <div class="faq-question" role="button" tabindex="0">How do I book an appointment?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Book online at any time through our Phorest booking page for the North Hills location. For Canonsburg appointments, please call us directly at 724-514-7231. Online booking is available 24/7 and lets you select your stylist, service, and preferred time.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question" role="button" tabindex="0">What areas do you serve?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Our North Hills location serves clients from across greater Pittsburgh including Shadyside, Lawrenceville, Squirrel Hill, South Hills, Cranberry Township, Wexford, Ross Township, McCandless, and Mt. Lebanon. Our Canonsburg location serves the South Hills and Washington County area.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question" role="button" tabindex="0">Do I need a consultation before getting extensions?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Yes. A consultation is required for hair extensions to ensure proper color matching, method selection, and hair ordering. Consultations allow us to plan your extension service for the best results and your specific hair type, density, and goals.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question" role="button" tabindex="0">What color brands do you use?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">We primarily use Wella Professionals color products. Our owner Derek Piekarski served on the North America Signature Artist Team for Wella and brings that deep product expertise directly to your service. We select color lines for their performance, consistency, and hair health outcomes.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question" role="button" tabindex="0">Do you offer services beyond hair?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Craft Collective Salon Group offers a full menu beyond hair including nail services (manicures, pedicures, gel, acrylics, extensions), skin care and facials, and lash extensions. We are a full-service salon destination.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

