      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">"I've been going to salons in Pittsburgh for over fifteen years, and nothing comes close to Craft Collective. Derek understood exactly what I wanted from a single consultation. My balayage has never looked this natural or lasted this long."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <p class="testimonial-name">Sarah M.</p>
            <p class="testimonial-detail">Balayage Client, North Hills</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">"The level of expertise here is just different. I came in with damaged, over-processed hair and they put together a plan to get me back to healthy blonde over a few visits. Patient, honest, and incredibly skilled."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <p class="testimonial-name">Megan K.</p>
            <p class="testimonial-detail">Blonding Client, Cranberry Township</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">"Found Craft Collective after moving from New York and I was worried I wouldn't find a salon on the same level. I was wrong. This team is world-class. The attention to detail, the atmosphere, the results -- it's all exceptional."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <p class="testimonial-name">Lauren T.</p>
            <p class="testimonial-detail">Color & Cut Client, Shadyside</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
