          <p class="testimonial-text">"I drive 45 minutes each way for my appointments because there is nobody else I trust with my extensions. The team at Craft Collective takes the time to do it right and my hair has never been healthier."</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <p class="testimonial-name">Jessica R.</p>
